      "span_text": "Similar to K5-N,OS(H) and IMW-K5, LMW-K5 derivatives abrogate FGF2-mediated attachment of FGFR1-expressing cells to neighboring HSPG-bearing cells, thus indicating their ability to prevent the formation of the HSPG/FGF2/FGFR ternary complex. [CITATION_2]"
